<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">4倍速算法，可用“折半调减法”进行速算。由于4=5-1，所以某数乘以4，只要将某数折半，扩大10倍再减去某数，便是其积。其口诀是：4乘某数先折半，然后再将某数减。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×4=a÷2×10-a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">136×4=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 136×4</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=136÷2×10-136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=68×10-136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=680-136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=544</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>